<HEAD>Boy Dies After Spending Four Hours In Freezer</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto CD4</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By JOE McDONALD</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>CLEVELAND (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
