hursday's $ 441 Earlier, in <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION>, gold dropped 48 cents an ounce to close at a bid of $ 440.05. Silver was quoted in <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> at a bid price of $ 7.30 late this morning, down from late Thursday's $ 7.35.
